{"tid":892011,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"其實狗應該飲生水（即係水喉水）定係熟水？","createTime":"2018-11-06T14:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T02:53:13.000Z","uid":93388,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4a5fd228a5dfdacfe27ff6b0c4af78b704d1f7a2","tid":892011,"uid":93388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"本身以前細個嗰陣都養過一隻狗，當時家人都係餵水喉水俾隻狗飲，一直都冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n到呢家養緊隻臘腸妹，都係俾水喉水佢飲，但我家姐今日突然又話水喉水有菌啊有呢樣嗰樣會搞到隻衰妹肚仔會生蟲，要轉俾熟水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網睇啲人都係有唔同講法，睇到頭都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下各位養狗嘅巴絲平時係俾隻狗飲生水定熟水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82026e15b7c1d7b2b90ad03608e532256916d609","tid":892011,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"我隻狗好中意自己走去飲馬桶水<br />\n每星期起碼一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e0c40c07c838d3e8dc87d648901f484a040574","tid":892011,"uid":99700,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"82026e15b7c1d7b2b90ad03608e532256916d609","tid":892011,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"我隻狗好中意自己走去飲馬桶水<br />\n每星期起碼一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"食屎狗冇屎食飲住水先"},{"pid":"fe277a4c4928f992eb9a810ee7bbe833c0b42751","tid":892011,"uid":144631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:37:07.000Z","msg":"你座大廈舊唔舊？<br />\n如果舊既 熟水 / 過濾水好啲"},{"pid":"2e443b56bd93a596b1642e2fa3de491e8